nance plan. Our current special offer starts at \u00a399 setup and \u00a315 a month for a single boutique \u2014 with no commission and no per-booking fees. See the <a href=\"/pricing/\">pricing page</a> for the full breakdown.</p>", "_id": "b0d6d36"}, {"tab_title": "Is this appointment software only for bridal shops?", "tab_content": "<p>It's built around how bridal boutiques actually work \u2014 consultations, fitting rooms, wedding dates and dress questions \u2014 but the same booking engine suits any appointment-based business that wants its own branded system rather than a shared platform.</p>", "_id": "ada45cc"}, {"tab_title": "Can brides book appointments from their phone?", "tab_content": "<p>Yes. The booking page works instantly on any phone, tablet or computer with nothing to download, and it's styled to match your boutique so it feels like part of your own website.</p>", "_id": "79c1012"}, {"tab_title": "How is this different from a generic booking widget or platform?", "tab_content": "<p>You get your own private system, branded to you and owned by you \u2014 not a shared third-party widget that charges a fee on every booking. There are no commissions and no platform subscriptions.</p>", "_id": "aeb94e4"}, {"tab_title": "Do I need any technical skills to run it?", "tab_content": "<p>No. We build it, brand it and set up your services and opening hours for you. Day to day you just manage bookings from a simple staff control panel, and we handle hosting, backups and updates.</p>", "_id": "eeb78c4"}], "title_color": "#2E332B", "tab_active_color": "#A78C46", "content_color": "#79806E", "title_typography_typography": "custom", "title_typography_font_family": "Cormorant Garamond", "title_typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 20, "sizes": []}, "title_typography_font_weight": "500", "content_typography_typography": "custom", "content_typography_font_family": "Jost", "content_typography_font_size": {"unit": "px", "size": 15.5, "sizes": []}, "content_typogra